Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.89,0:00:58.65,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)\fad(100,0)}This power which leaves even my hopes and future in the dust,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.65,0:01:01.57,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)}It knows no boundaries, has no meaning.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.57,0:01:10.52,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)\fad(0,100)}I lay my dreams where this power blazes with light.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.71,0:01:19.38,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)}If all I can do is look back at my past lit by my power,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.38,0:01:26.05,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)}I could destroy everything now.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.05,0:01:29.18,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)}The streets plunge into darkness.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.18,0:01:32.90,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)}How far will people resist?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.90,0:01:40.65,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)}I'm sure it would protect someone from that worsening pain.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.49,0:01:54.16,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)}A premonition of fate runs around my body at the speed of light.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.16,0:01:56.96,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)}Grab it — if it's your wish, leave none behind
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.96,0:02:00.72,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)}Shining as yourself,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.55,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)}I trust in the oath you made that day.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.55,0:02:13.06,op_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,718)}Because even the shining tears in your eyes make me strong.
