Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:40.65,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it would protect someone from that worsening pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:54.16,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,A premonition of fate runs around my body at the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:56.96,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab it — if it's your wish, leave none behind
