Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.61,0:00:07.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the first victim one week ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:17.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the graviton incidents have been increasing in power and scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't confirm any correlations between them in regards to time or location.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:31.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We completed psychometric investigations on the items, but still haven't found any clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:35.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prevent any further increase in victim count,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:39.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we must work with Antiskill to harden our guard and solve this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:28.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1.3}You were up late again investigating the graviton case last night, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:36.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're making no progress, we have to keep checking it over to see if we missed anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:40.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay to be passionate about work, but don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:57.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:47.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do worry that much about me, don't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:51.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, if we could just sleep together tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:53.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be better in no time!{Norg: 疲れが something :/}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:57.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly Onee-sama, you're so bashful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:16.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,AIM diffusion power fields are a phenomenon closely related to espers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:21.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,AIM stands for "An Involuntary Movement".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:27.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It refers to the weak force that espers emit subconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:33.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to feel using the five senses, and cannot be measured without using machinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:37.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, developments in this field have been remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go to shopping at Seventh Mist on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:48.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I have work at Judgment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay if we're quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say you're on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:57.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that this time, with the case we're working on being how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:00.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:09.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you lend us a bit of cash again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:21.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't returned the last... lot... have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We said we'd pay you back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get rich, that is.{出世払い -> promise to pay back when you become successful in life}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:37.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And isn't it your selling point to have no limits, no interest, and no deadline for repayment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:43.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go before Judgment gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:48.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They always come after things are over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Judgment...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:59.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to put up with this stuff because you guys are so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:03.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch.{Norg: 犯人フラグ？ｗ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we only had some kind of clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:17.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:23.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All we really know is the culprit must be a Level 4 or higher esper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:28.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody in the databank matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:32.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be an esper who attained greater powers very quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:33.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:36.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's doable in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be patient and check the items from the start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:59.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saten-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:13.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uiharu must be having a hard time, along with Kuroko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:18.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I invited her to go shopping today, but she turned me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:23.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no helping it until the bomber gets caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:30.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything feels so distant right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:33.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:39.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing how hard Uiharu and Shirai-san are working in Judgment, and you being so amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:41.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to think "What am I doing?"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't mean to sound so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:55.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking how things might change if I had powers too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:04.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had the Level Upper, then Level 5 wouldn't be such a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Level Upper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that urban legend we were talking about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:14.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's a tool that allows you to easily level up your powers. {Norg: Rare-candy! :D}{ポケモンをやった人がいる！　Σ(￣Д￣;)がーんっ!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:21.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Stripper Lady really existed so I thought maybe it might be around too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way it's real, right?{Norg: フラグ立ち、その２ｗ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all go?{Norg: go where? you vague biribiri-onna!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:37.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping together with Onee-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both off-duty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:42.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to Saten-san about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:45.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:49.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful for the offer, but I'm afraid I'll have to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do a little more investigation.{Norg: excuses...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:55.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:58.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.{Norg: why does the future-laptop sound like a PC from 10 years ago with an ultra clunky magnetic hard drive? >.>}{loose fan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A new world is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So Shirai-san said she couldn't come, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:49.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need some Judgment who couldn't save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:09.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not anything in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uiharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:14.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:18.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta da!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:19.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about these?{Norg: さてんさんの初春パンツフェチ　現る！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way no way no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wear something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:30.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have this on, you can show off to everyone when I flip up your skirt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:33.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want everyone to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't flip up my skirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:37.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Misaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Might you be looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:42.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:43.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could go for pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:55.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've looked around, but I can't find any good ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think this is so cute—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.23,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:09.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those pajamas, Uiharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:13.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would wear something so childish these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:17.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to wear something like this when I was in elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but not so much these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Middle schoolers wouldn't wear these!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:23.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm going to take a look at the swimsuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:33.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The swimsuits are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:33.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:36.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just pajamas, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else is going to be looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, now's my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see how they look for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:49.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing, Biribiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, I'm not allowed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:02.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Tokiwadai Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one with the bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:15.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you had a little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:21.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was looking for a clothing store, so I accompanied her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:25.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan took me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:30.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have stylish clothes like the people on TV too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:35.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're already stylishly cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike a certain shorts person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You picking a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:43.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish what we started right here! {check}{Norg: いつぞやの決着 I think the current trans is close enough}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:47.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you ever think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:52.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, do you really want to start something with so many people around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Onii-chan, I want to look at those!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:04.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:19.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, whenever he's around...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:32.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get all weird. {Norg: This line and the one above are kinda wrong. something like "Whenever he's around, I can't act like myself."}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:35.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gekotan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:39.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, they're nothing alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:59.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible there are multiple culprits with the same power?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:00.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd throw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:05.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see any other correlations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:09.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, another incident might occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find a clue, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:14.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine of our people have been injured already...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:22.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's too many?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:26.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think the target could be...{...aiming to hurt Judgement}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:32.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Satellites have confirmed the acceleration of gravitons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:37.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your cellphone, Uiharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:40.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, this is—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:41.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uiharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an update on the graviton case!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:49.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Academy City's surveillance satellites detected an explosive acceleration of gravitons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the location?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:53.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nearby Antiskill heading there already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:55.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get back to base now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said what's the location!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:01.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A clothing store in the 7th district — Seventh Mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventh Mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:08.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect, I'm already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll begin evacuation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uiharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Uiharu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:27.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've figured out the criminal's next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This store.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:35.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaka-san, could I ask you to assist with the evacuation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:37.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saten-san, you should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:40.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Uiharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The target this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an announcement to all customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:58.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to an electrical system failure in the store,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:02.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we're afraid we will have to close for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:06.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Store assistants will guide you to the exit.{Norg: check!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:09.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We apologize for the inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got here too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:11.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Biribiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:14.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't she with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:20.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be still inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:32.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uiharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've completed the evacuation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:36.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:41.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The only casualties have been Judgment members!{人的被害}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:45.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal's target is any Judgment within each location!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:49.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The target this time is you, Uiharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:52.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:00.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:05.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy with glasses asked me to give this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:06.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:13.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy it with my railgun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:16.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Another terrorist serial bombing attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:32.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There were people still in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a Judgment kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous, stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:42.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:48.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My power is gradually becoming stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a few more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:58.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those useless Judgment and those assholes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow them all awa—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:18.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really have to ask that do you, Bomber-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:22.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know what you're talking about—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:25.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that power is certainly impressive,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:32.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,there were no casualties, not even a scrape or bruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:34.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I used my full power on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:42.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... it looked like a huge explosion from the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:47.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant there was no way anyone inside could survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:58.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Railgun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's Tokiwadai's Ace, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:13.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I always end up getting beaten to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People like you are the bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Same with Judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:23.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People with power are all like that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:28.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Power this, power that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Clench your teeth! {raw, raw, fight da powah!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious why she hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:57.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People like you who use lack of power as an excuse are unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:04.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokiwadai's Railgun was originally a plain Level 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:09.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She reached Level 5 through sheer hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:18.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,even were she a Level 1, she would still stand against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:44.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You had me worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:45.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:49.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to Misaka-san — look, perfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:53.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tokiwadai Onee-chan saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:56.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:57.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:03.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For the area they were in to be totally unharmed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:07.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did she do that with her power?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:20.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really outdid yourself this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:30.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroko will do anything for you today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:35.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like washing your back, or giving you a massage, anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:38.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:43.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:22.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Back there, my railgun didn't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:36.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who really saved Uiharu-san and the kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:41.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:47.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ambushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:48.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:54.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like everyone thinks I'm the one who saved everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:57.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take the credit, you'd be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.88,0:23:00.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:05.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's safe, so there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.51,0:23:08.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares who did the saving? {かっっっっっっっっっこいいいいいいいいい！！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:18.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit the posing! {すかす to pose / to put on an air}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.11,0:23:23.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop pretending to be all cool like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And only in front of me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pisses me off!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:31.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that guy, always always always...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:32.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaahh, so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be turning red, Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:35.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next week—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.45,0:23:37.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's turning red?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:37.61,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.61,0:23:38.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The sunset...?
