Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:08.66,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's sad, it's not enough
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:15.21,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,the sunset dyes the city
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:23.42,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,moving like the clouds, not really going anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:30.93,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,when I realized, we were crying together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:37.31,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, dreams, flowers, rainbows and the wind, let's take it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.99,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ok, cheer up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:45.38,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:52.14,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only today, let's get past this now and not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:55.83,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,it's ok, don't hesitate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:22:01.86,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,let's keep walking on forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:07.04,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,right into the future.
